          text: "During a security incident, all communications about the incident must be coordinated through the incident response lead. Employees must not discuss incident details with unauthorized individuals, media, or on social media.\n\n[COMPANY_NAME] will notify affected individuals, regulators, and business partners as required by applicable laws and contractual obligations. Legal counsel will be consulted before any external notifications are issued. Internal status updates will be provided to executive leadership and affected departments at regular intervals throughout the response."
